## ðŸ“Š Performance Considerations

### Code Splitting

Features are lazy-loaded for optimal performance:

```typescript
// App-level route configuration
const ChatFeature = lazy(() => import('@/features/chat'));
const FilesFeature = lazy(() => import('@/features/files'));

function App() {
