- ðŸ” **Code Search**: Easier to locate and understand usage across the app
- âœ¨ **Central Styling**: Theming and layout behavior lives in one place

## Trigger Conditions
This rule is agent-requested or invoked manually when:
- ðŸ” A third-party component is found used directly in a page or feature
- ðŸ§¼ A cleanup/refactor is underway
- ðŸ§± A new component is added but not organized into the atomic system

## Best Practices
- Place all wrapped components in `src/ui/atoms`, `molecules`, `organisms`
- Avoid leaking third-party props outside the wrapper unless explicitly needed
- When in doubt, wrap it â€” even layout utilities like `Box`, `Flex`, `Grid`

